    "title": "Grofers is Hiring: E-commerce Executive (Entry-Level)",
    "description": "Join the Grofers family as a E-commerce Executive in Pune. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Grofers:\nGrofers is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Grofers!",
